data.description: Nicely landscaped grounds with cement patios front and back.  Low maintenance shrubbery on all sides o house and log.  Quiet neighborhood.  Very  comfortable and practical interior design.  Kitchen has highly functional island and is conducive for dinner entertaining.  Garage doors are painted to match rest of exterior  very closely.  In addition to stand AC, a fully ducted evaporative cooler keeps electric bills low in summer.
